    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"461\" data-end=\"504\">Sanctuary of Gaia (Action; 1/Long Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"504\" data-end=\"507\" />You create a haven even amid chaos.</p><p data-start=\"544\" data-end=\"670\">As an action, you emanate a calming aura with a <strong data-start=\"592\" data-end=\"610\">10-foot radius</strong> centered on you for <strong data-start=\"631\" data-end=\"643\">1 minute</strong>. While the aura is active:</p><ul data-start=\"672\" data-end=\"830\"><li data-start=\"672\" data-end=\"729\"><p data-start=\"674\" data-end=\"729\">Allies in the aura have <strong data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"728\">advantage on saving throws</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"830\"><p data-start=\"732\" data-end=\"830\">Hostile creatures have <strong data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"787\">disadvantage on attack rolls</strong> made against creatures <strong data-start=\"811\" data-end=\"829\">other than you</strong>.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"832\" data-end=\"908\"><strong data-start=\"832\" data-end=\"845\">Drawback:</strong> Once you use this feature, you gain <strong data-start=\"882\" data-end=\"907\">1 level of exhaustion</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"977\"><strong data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"926\">Restriction:</strong> You cannot activate this feature while <strong data-start=\"966\" data-end=\"976\">raging</strong>.</p><p></p><p>[GAROU_FEATURE] id=sanctuary-of-gaia</p>",
